3.21	Mourning_sickness	Mourning sickness	Mourning sickness is a collective emotional condition of "recreational grieving" by individuals at the death of murder victims or celebrities. Such celebrity deaths may be linked to hyper-attentive, intrusive and voyeuristic media coverage, which has been dubbed grief porn.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/18/Diana_trafalgar_square.jpg/250px-Diana_trafalgar_square.jpg
